{"title":"陕北纪行","authors":["钱昌照"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北纪行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱昌照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛川到处青青见麦苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入冬槐柳未全雕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛川三日添诗料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昼看塬沟夜宿窑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从洛川赴延安途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻车驰傍洛河滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乍上高坡直北看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过劳山见塔影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此心飞跃入延安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米脂高西沟水平梯田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳传统越千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农事从无一日闲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我到米脂开眼界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯田直上白云间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榆林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榆林城北霜如雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映日明沙别样黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往昔不毛边塞地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于今杨柳万千行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北大雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安排劳力在塬沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜灾荒又一秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里秦中风雪路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逢人便祝大丰收。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}